name: Athens
description: This is a still from a film I will soon be releasing. It's a photo of Athens from the Acropolis looking directly to the mountain that once held the Temple of Zeus. I'm releasing this image to help fundraise for the finalization of this project. Purchaser will be sent a private link to the completed film in the next couple of weeks, but the must reach me on twitter @gdrtweets to notify me of the purchase.
